dc_title_s: War Department installations :Fifth Service Command : a section of the strategic map of the United States reduced in scale /War Department, Fifth Service Command, Corps of Engineers.
dc_description_s: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights.; First revision March 1, 1943.; Map extends from Springfield, Ill. on the west to Martinsburg, W. Va. on the east and Chicago on the north to the Kentucky-Tennessee border on the south.
